{"word":"χαλέπτω","slug":"χαλέπτω","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<el><b>χαλέπτω</b></el> <el>(χᾰλέπτω,) </el><br/><b><a href='S:Etymology'>Etym.</a> </b>Causal of <a href='S:χαλεπαίνω'><el>χαλεπαίνω</el></a>\n<p/><div class='li500'><b>I. </b><i>to oppress, depress, crush</i>, <b><a href='S:Odyssey'>Od.</a></b>, <b><a href='S:Hesiod'>Hes.</a></b><p/></div><div class='li500'><b>II. </b><a href='S:passive signification'><a href='S:Passive Voice'>Pass.</a></a>, <el>χαλεφθείς τινι</el> <i>enraged at</i> one, <b><a href='S:Theognis'>Theogn.</a></b><p/></div><div class='li500'><b>III. </b><a href='S:intransitive'>intr.</a> <i>to be angry, vexed at</i>, <el>τινί</el> <b>Bion.</b><p/></div>"}]}